thread.title: Catherine E. Ziegler
thread.title_full: Redding Medical Inc. reviewed by Catherine E. Ziegler

author: Catherine E. Ziegler
title: Catherine E. Ziegler
text: I recently purchased a new stethoscope (Littman Cardiology IV) due to the fact that the piping in my previous stethoscope was tearing. I had it engraved and shipped TWO DAY. It arrived quickly and in excellent condition. This stethoscope is FANTASTIC!
